desc: Filth and rust have eaten away at this bed. Thankfully I'm not at all tired.
name: Wrecked Bed

desc: An old boiler. A dripping echoes from inside.
name: Wrecked Boiler

desc: A filthy chair. Insects skitter in and out of holes in the fabric.
name: Wrecked Chair

desc: No chance of this thing starting up.
name: Wrecked Console

desc: Scratching sounds from the inside... I think something has made a nest in there.
name: Wrecked Computer

desc: It looks like an old remote terminal.
name: Wrecked Terminal

desc: A antique crate, I wonder what's inside..
name: Wrecked Crate

desc: This door is almost rusted shut.
name: Wrecked Door

desc: The stale air produces little more than a creak from this old fan.
name: Wrecked Fan

desc: Once upon a time, a couple of these things could power a whole ship.
name: Wrecked Generator

desc: An old locker. Hey! There's a photo taped to the inside...
name: Wrecked Locker

desc: An old input panel. One of the keys has fallen off.
name: Wrecked Panel

desc: An old input panel, probably used to be used for security.
name: Small Wrecked Panel

desc: A smashed monitor, not much use now.
name: Wrecked Monitor

desc: A small damaged table.
name: Small Wrecked Table

desc: A rusty metal support.
name: Wrecked Support

desc: A battered old table. Still operational as far as tables go!
name: Wrecked Table

desc: A wrecked turbine, completely non-operational.
name: Wrecked Turbine

desc: A couple of wrecked turbines caked in dust.
name: Wrecked Turbines

desc: The screen sends out an ominous flickering light.
name: Wrecked Screen
